virtual async Task Nop.Services.Installation.InstallationService.InstallLanguagesAsync ( (string languagePackDownloadLink, int languagePackProgress)  languagePackInfo,

417  {
418  var localizationService = EngineContext.Current.Resolve<ILocalizationService>();
419 
420  var defaultCulture = new CultureInfo(NopCommonDefaults.DefaultLanguageCulture);
421  var defaultLanguage = new Language
422  {
423  Name = defaultCulture.TwoLetterISOLanguageName.ToUpper(),
424  LanguageCulture = defaultCulture.Name,
425  UniqueSeoCode = defaultCulture.TwoLetterISOLanguageName,
426  FlagImageFileName = $"{defaultCulture.Name.ToLower()[^2..]}.png",
427  Rtl = defaultCulture.TextInfo.IsRightToLeft,
428  Published = true,
429  DisplayOrder = 1
430  };
431  await InsertInstallationDataAsync(defaultLanguage);
432 
433  //Install locale resources for default culture
434  var directoryPath = _fileProvider.MapPath(NopInstallationDefaults.LocalizationResourcesPath);
435  var pattern = $"*.{NopInstallationDefaults.LocalizationResourcesFileExtension}";
436  foreach (var filePath in _fileProvider.EnumerateFiles(directoryPath, pattern))
437  {
438  using var streamReader = new StreamReader(filePath);
439  await localizationService.ImportResourcesFromXmlAsync(defaultLanguage, streamReader);
440  }
441 
442  if (cultureInfo == null || regionInfo == null || cultureInfo.Name == NopCommonDefaults.DefaultLanguageCulture)
443  return;
444 
445  var language = new Language
446  {
447  Name = cultureInfo.TwoLetterISOLanguageName.ToUpper(),
448  LanguageCulture = cultureInfo.Name,
449  UniqueSeoCode = cultureInfo.TwoLetterISOLanguageName,
450  FlagImageFileName = $"{regionInfo.TwoLetterISORegionName.ToLower()}.png",
451  Rtl = cultureInfo.TextInfo.IsRightToLeft,
452  Published = true,
453  DisplayOrder = 2
454  };
455  await InsertInstallationDataAsync(language);
456 
457  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(languagePackInfo.languagePackDownloadLink))
458  return;
459 
460  //download and import language pack
461  try
462  {
463  var httpClientFactory = EngineContext.Current.Resolve<IHttpClientFactory>();
464  var httpClient = httpClientFactory.CreateClient(NopHttpDefaults.DefaultHttpClient);
465  await using var stream = await httpClient.GetStreamAsync(languagePackInfo.languagePackDownloadLink);
466  using var streamReader = new StreamReader(stream);
467  await localizationService.ImportResourcesFromXmlAsync(language, streamReader);
468 
469  //set this language as default
470  language.DisplayOrder = 0;
471  await UpdateInstallationDataAsync(language);
472 
473  //save progress for showing in admin panel (only for first start)
474  await InsertInstallationDataAsync(new GenericAttribute
475  {
476  EntityId = language.Id,
477  Key = NopCommonDefaults.LanguagePackProgressAttribute,
478  KeyGroup = nameof(Language),
479  Value = languagePackInfo.languagePackProgress.ToString(),
480  StoreId = 0,
481  CreatedOrUpdatedDateUTC = DateTime.UtcNow
482  });
483  }
484  catch { }
485  }

7781  //reviews

7785  {

7787  continue;

virtual async Task<string> Nop.Services.Installation.InstallationService.ValidateSeNameAsync< T > ( T  entity,
string  seName 
)
protectedvirtual

Retorna
A task that represents the asynchronous operation

Restrições do Tipo
T :BaseEntity 
243  : BaseEntity
244  {
245  //duplicate of ValidateSeName method of \Nop.Services\Seo\UrlRecordService.cs (we cannot inject it here)
246  if (entity == null)
247  throw new ArgumentNullException(nameof(entity));
248 
249  //validation
250  var okChars = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz1234567890 _-";
251  seName = seName.Trim().ToLowerInvariant();
252 
253  var sb = new StringBuilder();
254  foreach (var c in seName.ToCharArray())
255  {
256  var c2 = c.ToString();
257  if (okChars.Contains(c2))
258  sb.Append(c2);
259  }
260 
261  seName = sb.ToString();
262  seName = seName.Replace(" ", "-");
263  while (seName.Contains("--"))
264  seName = seName.Replace("--", "-");
265  while (seName.Contains("__"))
266  seName = seName.Replace("__", "_");
267 
268  //max length
269  seName = CommonHelper.EnsureMaximumLength(seName, NopSeoDefaults.SearchEngineNameLength);
270 
271  //ensure this sename is not reserved yet
272  var i = 2;
273  var tempSeName = seName;
274  while (true)
275  {
276  //check whether such slug already exists (and that is not the current entity)
277 
278  var query = from ur in _urlRecordRepository.Table
279  where tempSeName != null && ur.Slug == tempSeName
280  select ur;
281  var urlRecord = await query.FirstOrDefaultAsync();
282 
283  var entityName = entity.GetType().Name;
284  var reserved = urlRecord != null && !(urlRecord.EntityId == entity.Id && urlRecord.EntityName.Equals(entityName, StringComparison.InvariantCultureIgnoreCase));
285  if (!reserved)
286  break;
287 
288  tempSeName = $"{seName}-{i}";
289  i++;
290  }
291 
292  seName = tempSeName;
293 
294  return seName;
295  }
